      <h1 class="art-h1">Gold and bullion as collateral: a practical guide</h1>
      <p class="art-lead">
        Physical gold can be a useful private asset, but it is not automatically good collateral. This
        guide explains how bullion is assessed for lending, including purity, ownership, storage,
        control, valuation, liquidity, legal enforceability and sale risk.
      </p>
      <div class="art-byline">
        <div class="art-author">
          <Image class="art-avatar" src={specialistImg} alt="" widths={[42, 84]} sizes="42px" format="webp" quality={80} />
